abstract: >-
  A co-owned operating kit for capable AI coding agents. It pairs a portable,
  vendor-neutral doctrine (token economics, durable context, goal and loop
  contracts, provenance, and memory) with an optional Claude Code enforced
  runtime that turns the doctrine's advisory conventions into hook-enforced
  usage and routing controls. The doctrine is portable prose and data; the
  enforced runtime is Claude Code specific.
